quran[7{c,v,t}:
5,114,"is par eesa Ibn maryam ne dua ki"" khudaaya! hamaray rab! hum par aasman se aik khawan nazil kar jo hamaray liye aur hamaray uglo pichlon ke liye khusi ka mauqa qarar paye aur teri taraf se aik nishani ho, hum ko rizaq day aur to behtareen Razaq hai """
5,115,"Allah ne jawab diya"" mein uss ko tum par nazil karne wala ho n, magar is ke baad jo tum mein se kufar kere ga usay mein aisi saza dun ga jo duniya mein kisi ko nah di hogi """
5,116,"gharz jab ( yeh ehsanaat yaad dila kar ) Allah farmaiye ga ke"" ae eesa Ibn maryam! kya to ne logon se kaha tha ke khuda ke siwa mujhe aur meri maa ko bhi khuda bana lau ?"" to woh jawab mein arz kere ga ke"" subhan Allah ! mera yeh kaam nah tha ke woh baat kehta jis ke kehnay ka mujhe haq nah tha, agar mein ne aisi baat kahi hoti, to aap ko zaroor ilm hota, aap jantay hain jo kuch mere dil mein hai aur mein nahi jaanta jo kuch aap ke dil mein hai, aap to saari posheeda haqeeqaton ke aalam hain"
5,117,"mein ne unn se uss ke siwa kuch nahi kaha jis ka aap ne hukum diya tha, yeh ke Allah ki bandagi karo jo mera rab bhi hai aur tumhara rab bhi mein usi waqt taq un ka nigaran tha jab taq ke mein un ke darmain tha jab aap ne mujhe wapas bulaa liya to aap un par nigaran thay aur aap to saari hi cheezon par nigaran hain"
5,118,"ab agar aap inhen saza den to woh aap ke bande hain aur agar maaf kar den to aap ghalib aur Dana hain """
5,119,"tab Allah farmaiye ga"" yeh woh din hai jis mein schon ko unn ki sachaai naffa deti hai, un ke liye aisay baagh hain jin ke neechay nhrin beh rahi hain, yahan woh hamesha rahen ge, Allah un se raazi howa aur woh Allah se, yahi barri kamyabi hai """
5,120,zameen aur asmano aur tamam mojoodaat ki badshshi Allah hi ke liye hai aur woh har cheez par qudrat rakhta hai
